public CloningInfo(string sourceWebAppId, string correlationId = null, bool ? overwrite = null, bool ? cloneCustomHostNames = null, bool ? cloneSourceControl = null, string hostingEnvironment = null, IDictionary<string, string> appSettingsOverrides = null, bool ? configureLoadBalancing = null, string trafficManagerProfileId = null, string trafficManagerProfileName = null)Public Sub New(sourceWebAppId As String, correlationId As String = Nothing, overwrite As Boolean? = Nothing, cloneCustomHostNames As Boolean? = Nothing, cloneSourceControl As Boolean? = Nothing, hostingEnvironment As String = Nothing, appSettingsOverrides As IDictionary(Of String, String) = Nothing, configureLoadBalancing As Boolean? = Nothing, trafficManagerProfileId As String = Nothing, trafficManagerProfileName As String = Nothing)
Parameters
sourceWebAppId
String String

ARM resource ID of the source app. App resource ID is of the form /subscriptions/{subId}/resourceGroups/{resourceGroupName}/providers/Microsoft.Web/sites/{siteName} for production slots and /subscriptions/{subId}/resourceGroups/{resourceGroupName}/providers/Microsoft.Web/sites/{siteName}/slots/{slotName} for other slots.

correlationId
String String

Correlation ID of cloning operation. This ID ties multiple cloning operations together to use the same snapshot.

overwrite
Nullable<Boolean> Nullable(Of Boolean)

<code>true</code> to overwrite destination app; otherwise, <code>false</code>.

cloneCustomHostNames
Nullable<Boolean> Nullable(Of Boolean)

<code>true</code> to clone custom hostnames from source app; otherwise, <code>false</code>.

cloneSourceControl
Nullable<Boolean> Nullable(Of Boolean)

<code>true</code> to clone source control from source app; otherwise, <code>false</code>.

hostingEnvironment
String String

App Service Environment.

appSettingsOverrides
IDictionary<String, String> IDictionary(Of String, String)

Application setting overrides for cloned app. If specified, these settings override the settings cloned from source app. Otherwise, application settings from source app are retained.

configureLoadBalancing
Nullable<Boolean> Nullable(Of Boolean)

<code>true</code> to configure load balancing for source and destination app.

trafficManagerProfileId
String String

ARM resource ID of the Traffic Manager profile to use, if it exists. Traffic Manager resource ID is of the form /subscriptions/{subId}/resourceGroups/{resourceGroupName}/providers/Microsoft.Network/trafficManagerProfiles/{profileName}.

trafficManagerProfileName
String String

Name of Traffic Manager profile to create. This is only needed if Traffic Manager profile does not already exist.
